d well.\\\"\", \"from\": 1281, \"to\": 1347, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Looking ahead, the Cypriot has set her sights on the 2028 Los Angeles Games, where she hopes to win a medal.\", \"from\": 1349, \"to\": 1457, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1368, \"end\": 1375, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprus\", \"score\": 0.926169300075969, \"rank\": 0.043116061563517175, \"text\": \"Cypriot\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Cyprus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"After competing in Italy this October, Lappa plans to immediately start preparations for the next Olympics.\", \"from\": 1458, \"to\": 1565, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1477, \"end\": 1482, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"score\": 0.7272156439698354, \"rank\": 0.3479123733834412, \"text\": \"Italy\", \"types\": [\"Q476028\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Italy_national_football_team\"}, {\"begin\": 1497, \"end\": 1502, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrapper_(clothing)\", \"score\": 0.7501902424343043, \"rank\": 0.1791245791245716, \"text\": \"Lappa\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrapper_(clothing)\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Wrapper_(clothing)\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But for now, her focus is on representing Cyprus with pride at the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 1567, \"to\": 1649, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"I will do my best to honour Cyprus, our flag, and our island at the 2024 Olympic Games,\\\" she said.\", \"from\": 1651, \"to\": 1750, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Julia Stern is a student at Princeton University.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1801, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1752, \"end\": 1757, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Julia_the_Elder\", \"score\": 0.9999998155019681, \"rank\":